    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with the naturally aspirated powerplant delivering a linear torque curve and a crisp 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally pristine, showing no signs of subframe stress. Preventative maintenance is fully documented, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The exterior retains its factory luster with perfect panel gaps and zero paint correction required, while the Novillo leather interior remains supple and free of bolster wear. A definitive turn-key enthusiast specimen.",
