      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one, appearing in a condition that is truly showroom-fresh. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, all protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or aging, and every piece of switchgear operates with a satisfying, factory-new tactile feel. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history, including a recent major interval service performed by master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road debris, reflecting its life of leisure. With a clean title, zero accidents, and a fresh set of high-performance tires, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to own a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
